{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I thought I would read poems I have that relate to the subject"},{"time":3000,"text":"of youth and age."},{"time":6000,"text":"I was sort of astonished to find out how many I have actually."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9000,"text":"The first one is dedicated to"},{"time":11000,"text":"Spencer, and his grandmother, who was shocked by his work."},{"time":17000,"text":"My poem is called \"Dirt.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":20000,"text":"My grandmother is washing my mouth out with soap;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":24000,"text":"half a long century gone"}]},{"cues":[{"time":26000,"text":"and still she comes at me"}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"with that thick cruel yellow bar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31000,"text":"All because of a word I said,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":34000,"text":"not even said really, only repeated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37000,"text":"But \"Open,\" she says, \"open up!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":39000,"text":"her hand clawing at my head."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43000,"text":"I know now her life was hard;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":45000,"text":"she lost three children as babies,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48000,"text":"then her husband died too,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":50000,"text":"leaving young sons, and no money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53000,"text":"She'd stand me in the sink to pee"}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"because there was never room in the toilet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58000,"text":"But oh, her soap!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":60000,"text":"Might its bitter burning have been"},{"time":62000,"text":"what made me a poet?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":65000,"text":"The street she lived on was unpaved,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":68000,"text":"her flat, two cramped rooms and a fetid kitchen"}]},{"cues":[{"time":71000,"text":"where she stalked and caught me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74000,"text":"Dare I admit that after she did it"}]},{"cues":[{"time":77000,"text":"I never really loved her again?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":80000,"text":"She lived to a hundred,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":82000,"text":"even then. All along it was the sadness, the squalor,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":87000,"text":"but I never, until now"}]},{"cues":[{"time":89000,"text":"loved her again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93000,"text":"When that was published in a magazine"},{"time":95000,"text":"I got an irate letter from my uncle."},{"time":99000,"text":"\"You have maligned a great woman.\""},{"time":105000,"text":"It took some diplomacy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111000,"text":"This is called \"The Dress.\""},{"time":113000,"text":"It's a longer poem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115000,"text":"In those days,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":117000,"text":"those days which exist for me only"},{"time":119000,"text":"as the most elusive memory now,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"when often the first sound you'd hear in the morning"},{"time":125000,"text":"would be a storm of birdsong,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":127000,"text":"then the soft clop of the hooves"},{"time":129000,"text":"of the horse hauling a milk wagon down your block,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":133000,"text":"and the last sound at night as likely as not"}]},{"cues":[{"time":136000,"text":"would be your father pulling up in his car,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":139000,"text":"having worked late again, always late,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":142000,"text":"and going heavily down to the cellar, to the furnace,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":145000,"text":"to shake out the ashes and damp the draft"},{"time":148000,"text":"before he came upstairs to fall into bed --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":152000,"text":"in those long-ago days,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":154000,"text":"women, my mother, my friends' mothers,"},{"time":157000,"text":"our neighbors, all the women I knew --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":160000,"text":"wore, often much of the day,"},{"time":162000,"text":"what were called housedresses,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":164000,"text":"cheap, printed, pulpy,"},{"time":166000,"text":"seemingly purposefully shapeless"},{"time":169000,"text":"light cotton shifts that you wore over your nightgown"}]},{"cues":[{"time":172000,"text":"and, when you had to go look for a child,"},{"time":175000,"text":"hang wash on the line,"},{"time":177000,"text":"or run down to the grocery store on the corner,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":180000,"text":"under a coat,"},{"time":182000,"text":"the twisted hem of the nightgown"},{"time":184000,"text":"always lank and yellowed,"},{"time":186000,"text":"dangling beneath."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189000,"text":"More than the curlers some of the women"},{"time":191000,"text":"seemed constantly to have in their hair"},{"time":194000,"text":"in preparation for some great event --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":196000,"text":"a ball, one would think --"},{"time":198000,"text":"that never came to pass;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":200000,"text":"more than the way most women's faces"},{"time":202000,"text":"not only were never made up during the day,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":205000,"text":"but seemed scraped, bleached,"},{"time":208000,"text":"and, with their plucked eyebrows, scarily masklike;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":211000,"text":"more than all that it was those dresses"},{"time":215000,"text":"that made women so unknowable and forbidding,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"adepts of enigmas to which men could have no access,"},{"time":222000,"text":"and boys no conception."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226000,"text":"Only later would I see the dresses also"},{"time":229000,"text":"as a proclamation:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":231000,"text":"that in your dim kitchen, your laundry,"},{"time":235000,"text":"your bleak concrete yard,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":237000,"text":"what you revealed of yourself"},{"time":239000,"text":"was a fabulation;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":241000,"text":"your real sensual nature,"},{"time":243000,"text":"veiled in those sexless vestments,"},{"time":246000,"text":"was utterly your dominion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249000,"text":"In those days, one hid much else as well:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":253000,"text":"grown men didn't embrace one another,"},{"time":255000,"text":"unless someone had died,"},{"time":257000,"text":"and not always then; you shook hands"}]},{"cues":[{"time":260000,"text":"or, at a ball game, thumped your friend's back"},{"time":263000,"text":"and exchanged blows meant to be codes for affection;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":267000,"text":"once out of childhood you'd never again know"},{"time":270000,"text":"the shock of your father's whiskers on your cheek,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":273000,"text":"not until mores at last had evolved,"},{"time":277000,"text":"and you could hug another man, then hold on for a moment,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":280000,"text":"then even kiss (your fathers bristles"},{"time":283000,"text":"white and stiff now)."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286000,"text":"What release finally, the embrace:"},{"time":289000,"text":"though we were wary -- it seemed so audacious --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":293000,"text":"how much unspoken joy there was"},{"time":295000,"text":"in that affirmation of equality and communion,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":298000,"text":"no matter how much misunderstanding"},{"time":302000,"text":"and pain had passed between you by then."}]},{"cues":[{"time":306000,"text":"We knew so little in those days,"},{"time":309000,"text":"as little as now, I suppose"},{"time":311000,"text":"about healing those hurts:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":313000,"text":"even the women, in their best dresses,"},{"time":316000,"text":"with beads and sequins sewn on the bodices,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":319000,"text":"even in lipstick and mascara,"},{"time":321000,"text":"their hair aflow,"},{"time":323000,"text":"could only stand wringing their hands,"},{"time":325000,"text":"begging for peace,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":327000,"text":"while father and son, like thugs,"},{"time":329000,"text":"like thieves, like Romans,"},{"time":332000,"text":"simmered and hissed and hated,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":334000,"text":"inflicting sorrows that endured,"},{"time":337000,"text":"the worst anyway,"},{"time":339000,"text":"through the kiss and embrace,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":341000,"text":"bleeding from brother to brother,"},{"time":343000,"text":"into the generations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346000,"text":"In those days there was still countryside"},{"time":349000,"text":"close to the city, farms, cornfields, cows;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":353000,"text":"even not far from our building"},{"time":355000,"text":"with its blurred brick and long shadowy hallway"}]},{"cues":[{"time":358000,"text":"you could find tracts with hills and trees"},{"time":361000,"text":"you could pretend were mountains and forests."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365000,"text":"Or you could go out by yourself"},{"time":367000,"text":"even to a half-block-long empty lot,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":370000,"text":"into the bushes: like a creature of leaves you'd lurk,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":374000,"text":"crouched, crawling, simplified, savage, alone;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":379000,"text":"already there was wanting to be simpler,"},{"time":383000,"text":"wanting, when they called you,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":386000,"text":"never to go back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":401000,"text":"This is another longish one,"},{"time":403000,"text":"about the old and the young."},{"time":406000,"text":"It actually happened right at the time we met."},{"time":408000,"text":"Part of the poem takes place in"},{"time":412000,"text":"space we shared and time we shared."}]},{"cues":[{"time":415000,"text":"It's called \"The Neighbor.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":417000,"text":"Her five horrid, deformed little dogs"},{"time":421000,"text":"who incessantly yap on the roof under my window."}]},{"cues":[{"time":425000,"text":"Her cats, God knows how many,"},{"time":427000,"text":"who must piss on her rugs --"},{"time":429000,"text":"her landing's a sickening reek."}]},{"cues":[{"time":432000,"text":"Her shadow once, fumbling the chain on her door,"},{"time":436000,"text":"then the door slamming fearfully shut,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":439000,"text":"only the barking and the music -- jazz --"},{"time":442000,"text":"filtering as it does, day and night into the hall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447000,"text":"The time it was Chris Connor singing \"Lush Life\" --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":450000,"text":"how it brought back my college sweetheart,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":453000,"text":"my first real love, who -- till I left her --"},{"time":457000,"text":"played the same record."}]},{"cues":[{"time":459000,"text":"And head on my shoulder, hand on my thigh,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":463000,"text":"sang sweetly along, of regrets and depletions"},{"time":467000,"text":"she was too young for,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":469000,"text":"as I was too young, later, to believe in her pain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":473000,"text":"It startled, then bored, then repelled me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":478000,"text":"My starting to fancy she'd ended up in this fire-trap"},{"time":481000,"text":"in the Village, that my neighbor was her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":484000,"text":"My thinking we'd meet, recognize one another,"},{"time":487000,"text":"become friends, that I'd accomplish a penance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491000,"text":"My seeing her, it wasn't her, at the mailbox."}]},{"cues":[{"time":496000,"text":"Gray-yellow hair, army pants under a nightgown,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":500000,"text":"her turning away, hiding her ravaged face"},{"time":503000,"text":"in her hands, muttering an inappropriate \"Hi.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":508000,"text":"Sometimes there are frightening goings-on in the stairwell."}]},{"cues":[{"time":512000,"text":"A man shouting, \"Shut up!\" The dogs frantically snarling,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":516000,"text":"claws scrabbling, then her -- her voice"},{"time":519000,"text":"hoarse, harsh, hollow,"},{"time":521000,"text":"almost only a tone,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":523000,"text":"incoherent, a note, a squawk,"},{"time":526000,"text":"bone on metal, metal gone molten,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":528000,"text":"calling them back,"},{"time":530000,"text":"\"Come back darlings, come back dear ones."},{"time":533000,"text":"My sweet angels, come back.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":537000,"text":"Medea she was, next time I saw her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":540000,"text":"Sorceress, tranced, ecstatic,"},{"time":543000,"text":"stock-still on the sidewalk"}]},{"cues":[{"time":545000,"text":"ragged coat hanging agape,"},{"time":548000,"text":"passersby flowing around her,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":550000,"text":"her mouth torn suddenly open"},{"time":552000,"text":"as though in a scream,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":554000,"text":"silently though, as though only in her brain"},{"time":557000,"text":"or breast had it erupted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":559000,"text":"A cry so pure, practiced, detached,"},{"time":563000,"text":"it had no need of a voice,"},{"time":566000,"text":"or could no longer bear one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":568000,"text":"These invisible links that allure,"},{"time":571000,"text":"these transfigurations, even of anguish, that hold us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576000,"text":"The girl, my old love,"},{"time":578000,"text":"the last lost time I saw her"}]},{"cues":[{"time":580000,"text":"when she came to find me at a party,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":583000,"text":"her drunkenly stumbling, falling,"},{"time":585000,"text":"sprawling, skirt hiked, eyes veined red,"},{"time":589000,"text":"swollen with tears, her shame,"},{"time":592000,"text":"her dishonor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594000,"text":"My ignorant, arrogant coarseness,"},{"time":597000,"text":"my secret pride, my turning away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":601000,"text":"Still life on a rooftop,"},{"time":603000,"text":"dead trees in barrels, a bench broken,"},{"time":607000,"text":"dogs, excrement, sky."}]},{"cues":[{"time":609000,"text":"What pathways through pain,"},{"time":611000,"text":"what junctures of vulnerability,"},{"time":614000,"text":"what crossings and counterings?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":616000,"text":"Too many lives in our lives already,"},{"time":619000,"text":"too many chances for sorrow,"},{"time":621000,"text":"too many unaccounted-for pasts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":624000,"text":"\"Behold me,\" the god of frenzied,"},{"time":626000,"text":"inexhaustible love says,"},{"time":629000,"text":"rising in bloody splendor, \"Behold me.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":634000,"text":"Her making her way"},{"time":636000,"text":"down the littered vestibule stairs,"},{"time":638000,"text":"one agonized step at a time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":641000,"text":"My holding the door."}]},{"cues":[{"time":643000,"text":"Her crossing the fragmented tiles,"},{"time":645000,"text":"faltering at the step to the street,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":648000,"text":"droning, not looking at me,"},{"time":650000,"text":"\"Can you help me?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":652000,"text":"Taking my arm, leaning lightly against me."},{"time":656000,"text":"Her wavering step into the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":659000,"text":"Her whispering, \"Thanks love.\" Lightly, lightly against me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":668000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":677000,"text":"I think I'll lighten up a little."},{"time":679000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":681000,"text":"Another, different kind of poem of youth and age."}]},{"cues":[{"time":685000,"text":"It's called \"Gas.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":687000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":689000,"text":"Wouldn't it be nice, I think,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":691000,"text":"when the blue-haired lady in the doctor's waiting room"},{"time":694000,"text":"bends over the magazine table"}]},{"cues":[{"time":697000,"text":"and farts, just a little,"},{"time":699000,"text":"and violently blushes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":702000,"text":"Wouldn't it be nice if intestinal gas"},{"time":704000,"text":"came embodied in visible clouds,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":707000,"text":"so she could see that her really quite inoffensive pop"},{"time":710000,"text":"had only barely grazed my face"}]},{"cues":[{"time":712000,"text":"before it drifted away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":714000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":716000,"text":"Besides, for this to have happened now"},{"time":718000,"text":"is a nice coincidence. Because not an hour ago,"},{"time":721000,"text":"while we were on our walk,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":723000,"text":"my dog was startled by a backfire"},{"time":725000,"text":"and jumped straight up like a horse bucking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":728000,"text":"And that brought back to me the stable"},{"time":730000,"text":"I worked on weekends when I was 12,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":732000,"text":"and a splendid piebald stallion,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":735000,"text":"who whenever he was mounted would buck just like that,"},{"time":738000,"text":"though more hugely of course,"},{"time":741000,"text":"enormous, gleaming, resplendent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":743000,"text":"And the woman, her face abashedly buried"},{"time":746000,"text":"in her \"Elle\" now, reminded me --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":748000,"text":"I'd forgotten that not the least part of my awe"},{"time":751000,"text":"consisted of the fact that with every jump he took"}]},{"cues":[{"time":755000,"text":"the horse would powerfully fart."}]},{"cues":[{"time":757000,"text":"Phwap! Phwap! Phwap!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":759000,"text":"Something never mentioned"},{"time":761000,"text":"in the dozens of books about horses"},{"time":763000,"text":"and their riders I devoured in those days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":766000,"text":"All that savage grandeur,"},{"time":769000,"text":"the steely glinting hooves,"},{"time":771000,"text":"the eruptions driven from the creature's mighty innards,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":775000,"text":"breath stopped, heart stopped, nostrils madly flared,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":780000,"text":"I didn't know if I wanted to break him, or be him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":785000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":787000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":797000,"text":"This is called \"Thirst.\""},{"time":802000,"text":"Many -- most of my poems actually"},{"time":804000,"text":"are urban poems. I happen to be reading a bunch that aren't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":808000,"text":"\"Thirst.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":810000,"text":"Here was my relation with the woman who lived all last autumn and winter,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":814000,"text":"day and night, on a bench"},{"time":816000,"text":"in the 103rd Street subway station,"},{"time":819000,"text":"until finally one day she vanished."}]},{"cues":[{"time":822000,"text":"We regarded each other, scrutinized one another."}]},{"cues":[{"time":826000,"text":"Me shyly, obliquely, trying not to be furtive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":830000,"text":"She boldly, unblinkingly, even pugnaciously,"},{"time":834000,"text":"wrathfully even, when her bottle was empty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":839000,"text":"I was frightened of her. I felt like a child."}]},{"cues":[{"time":842000,"text":"I was afraid some repressed part of myself"},{"time":845000,"text":"would go out of control, and I'd be forever entrapped"}]},{"cues":[{"time":848000,"text":"in the shocking seethe of her stench."}]},{"cues":[{"time":852000,"text":"Not excrement merely, not merely surface"},{"time":855000,"text":"and orifice going unwashed,"},{"time":857000,"text":"rediffusion of rum,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":859000,"text":"there was will in it,"},{"time":861000,"text":"and intention, power and purpose --"},{"time":863000,"text":"a social, ethical rage and rebellion --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":867000,"text":"despair too, though, grief, loss."}]},{"cues":[{"time":872000,"text":"Sometimes I'd think I should take her home with me,"},{"time":874000,"text":"bathe her, comfort her, dress her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":877000,"text":"She wouldn't have wanted me to, I would think."},{"time":880000,"text":"Instead, I'd step into my train."}]},{"cues":[{"time":883000,"text":"How rich I would think, is the lexicon"},{"time":886000,"text":"of our self-absolving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":888000,"text":"How enduring, our bland fatal assurance"},{"time":891000,"text":"that reflection is righteousness being accomplished."}]},{"cues":[{"time":896000,"text":"The dance of our glances,"},{"time":898000,"text":"the clash, pulling each other through"},{"time":901000,"text":"our perceptual punctures,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":903000,"text":"then holocaust, holocaust,"},{"time":905000,"text":"host on host of ill, injured presences,"},{"time":909000,"text":"squandered, consumed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":913000,"text":"Her vigil somewhere I know continues."}]},{"cues":[{"time":916000,"text":"Her occupancy, her absolute, faithful attendance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":921000,"text":"The dance of our glances, challenge, abdication,"},{"time":925000,"text":"effacement, the perfume of our consternation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":932000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":940000,"text":"This is a newer poem, a brand new poem."},{"time":944000,"text":"The title is \"This Happened.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":947000,"text":"A student, a young woman"},{"time":950000,"text":"in a fourth-floor hallway of her lycee,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":953000,"text":"perched on the ledge of an open window"},{"time":955000,"text":"chatting with friends between classes;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":959000,"text":"a teacher passes and chides her,"},{"time":961000,"text":"\"Be careful, you might fall,\""},{"time":963000,"text":"almost banteringly chides her,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":966000,"text":"\"You might fall,\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":968000,"text":"and the young woman, 18, a girl really,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":971000,"text":"though she wouldn't think that,"},{"time":973000,"text":"as brilliant as she is, first in her class,"},{"time":976000,"text":"and \"Beautiful, too,\" she's often told,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":979000,"text":"smiles back, and leans into the open window,"},{"time":983000,"text":"which wouldn't even be open if it were winter --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":986000,"text":"if it were winter someone would have closed it (\"Close it!\") --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":990000,"text":"leans into the window, farther, still smiling,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":994000,"text":"farther and farther, though it takes less time"},{"time":997000,"text":"than this, really an instant, and lets herself fall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1002000,"text":"Herself fall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1005000,"text":"A casual impulse, a fancy,"},{"time":1008000,"text":"never thought of until now, hardly thought of even now ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1012000,"text":"No, more than impulse or fancy,"},{"time":1015000,"text":"the girl knows what she's doing,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1017000,"text":"the girl means something,"},{"time":1019000,"text":"the girl means to mean,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1021000,"text":"because it occurs to her in that instant,"},{"time":1024000,"text":"that beautiful or not, bright yes or no,"},{"time":1027000,"text":"she's not who she is,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1029000,"text":"she's not the person she is,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1031000,"text":"and the reason, she suddenly knows,"},{"time":1033000,"text":"is that there's been so much premeditation"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1036000,"text":"where she is, so much plotting and planning,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1039000,"text":"there's hardly a person where she is,"},{"time":1042000,"text":"or if there is, it's not her, or not wholly her,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1046000,"text":"it's a self inhabited, lived in by her,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1050000,"text":"and seemingly even as she thinks it"},{"time":1052000,"text":"she knows what's been missing:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1054000,"text":"grace,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1056000,"text":"not premeditation but grace,"},{"time":1058000,"text":"a kind of being in the world spontaneously,"},{"time":1062000,"text":"with grace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1064000,"text":"Weightfully upon me was the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1067000,"text":"Weightfully this self which graced the world"},{"time":1070000,"text":"yet never wholly itself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1073000,"text":"Weightfully this self which weighed upon me,"},{"time":1076000,"text":"the release from which is what I desire"},{"time":1079000,"text":"and what I achieve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1081000,"text":"And the girl remembers, in this infinite instant"},{"time":1085000,"text":"already now so many times divided,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1088000,"text":"the sadness she felt once,"},{"time":1090000,"text":"hardly knowing she felt it,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1092000,"text":"to merely inhabit herself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1094000,"text":"Yes, the girl falls, absurd to fall,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1097000,"text":"even the earth with its compulsion"},{"time":1100000,"text":"to take unto itself all that falls"},{"time":1103000,"text":"must know that falling is absurd,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1105000,"text":"yet the girl falling isn't myself,"},{"time":1108000,"text":"or she is myself,"},{"time":1110000,"text":"but a self I took of my own volition unto myself."},{"time":1114000,"text":"Forever. With grace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1118000,"text":"This happened."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1121000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1129000,"text":"I'll read just one more. I don't usually say that."},{"time":1131000,"text":"I like to just end."},{"time":1133000,"text":"But I'm afraid that Ricky will come out here"},{"time":1136000,"text":"and shake his fist at me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1140000,"text":"This is called \"Old Man,\" appropriately enough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1144000,"text":"\"Special: big tits,\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1146000,"text":"Says the advertisement for a soft-core magazine"},{"time":1149000,"text":"on our neighborhood newsstand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1151000,"text":"But forget her breasts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1153000,"text":"A lush, fresh-lipped blond,"},{"time":1156000,"text":"skin glowing gold, sprawls there,"},{"time":1159000,"text":"resplendent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1161000,"text":"60 nearly, yet these hardly tangible,"},{"time":1164000,"text":"hardly better than harlots, can still stir me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1169000,"text":"Maybe a coming of age in the"},{"time":1171000,"text":"American sensual darkness,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1173000,"text":"never seeing an unsmudged nipple,"},{"time":1175000,"text":"an uncensored vagina,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1177000,"text":"has left me forever infected"},{"time":1180000,"text":"with an unquenchable lust of the eye."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1183000,"text":"Always that erotic murmur,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1185000,"text":"I'm hardly myself"},{"time":1187000,"text":"if I'm not in a state of incipient desire."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1191000,"text":"God knows though,"},{"time":1193000,"text":"there are worse twists your obsessions can take."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1196000,"text":"Last year in Israel, a young ultra-orthodox Rabbi"},{"time":1200000,"text":"guiding some teenage girls through the Shrine of the Shoah"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1204000,"text":"forbade them to look in one room."},{"time":1207000,"text":"Because there were images in it he said were licentious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1211000,"text":"The display was a photo. Men and women stripped naked,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1215000,"text":"some trying to cover their genitals,"},{"time":1217000,"text":"others too frightened to bother,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1219000,"text":"lined up in snow"},{"time":1221000,"text":"waiting to be shot and thrown into a ditch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1224000,"text":"The girls, to my horror,"},{"time":1227000,"text":"averted their gaze."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1229000,"text":"What carnal mistrust had their teacher taught them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1233000,"text":"Even that though. Another confession:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1237000,"text":"Once in a book on pre-war Poland,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1240000,"text":"a studio portrait, an absolute angel,"},{"time":1244000,"text":"an absolute angel with tormented, tormenting eyes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1246000,"text":"I kept finding myself at her page."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1249000,"text":"That she died in the camps made her --"},{"time":1252000,"text":"I didn't dare wonder why --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1255000,"text":"more present, more precious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1258000,"text":"Died in the camps, that too people --"},{"time":1261000,"text":"or Jews anyway --"},{"time":1263000,"text":"kept from their children back then."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1265000,"text":"But it was like sex, you didn't have to be told."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1269000,"text":"Sex and death, how close they can seem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1273000,"text":"So constantly conscious now of death moving towards me,"},{"time":1277000,"text":"sometimes I think I confound them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1280000,"text":"My wife's loveliness almost consumes me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1283000,"text":"My passion for her goes beyond reasonable bounds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1286000,"text":"When we make love, her holding me"},{"time":1289000,"text":"everywhere all around me,"},{"time":1291000,"text":"I'm there and not there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1293000,"text":"My mind teems, jumbles of faces, voices, impressions,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1297000,"text":"I live my life over, as though I were drowning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1302000,"text":"Then I am drowning, in despair"},{"time":1305000,"text":"at having to leave her,"},{"time":1307000,"text":"this, everything, all,"},{"time":1309000,"text":"unbearable, awful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1312000,"text":"Still, to be able to die"},{"time":1315000,"text":"with no special contrition,"},{"time":1317000,"text":"not having been slaughtered, or enslaved."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1320000,"text":"And not having to know history's next"},{"time":1323000,"text":"mad rage or regression,"},{"time":1325000,"text":"it might be a relief."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1328000,"text":"No. Again, no."},{"time":1330000,"text":"I don't mean that for a moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1332000,"text":"What I mean is the world holds me so tightly --"},{"time":1335000,"text":"the good and the bad --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1337000,"text":"my own follies and weakness"},{"time":1339000,"text":"that even this counterfeit Venus"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1342000,"text":"with her sham heat, and her bosom probably plumped"},{"time":1345000,"text":"with gel, so moves me"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1348000,"text":"my breath catches."},{"time":1350000,"text":"Vamp. Siren. Seductress."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1353000,"text":"How much more she reveals"},{"time":1355000,"text":"in her glare of ink than she knows."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1358000,"text":"How she incarnates"},{"time":1360000,"text":"our desperate human need for regard,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1363000,"text":"our passion to live in beauty,"},{"time":1366000,"text":"to be beauty, to be cherished by glances,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1370000,"text":"if by no more, of something like love,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1374000,"text":"or love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1376000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1378000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}